OL,4,Cfrom having civil partnership amid new
OL,5,Claw
OL,7,FSerial killer Levi Bellfield has been
OL,8,Fblocked from having a civil
OL,9,Fpartnership, after a new law came into
OL,10,Fforce stopping the most serious
OL,11,Foffenders getting married behind bars.
OL,13,FBellfield is serving two whole life
OL,14,Forders for killing 13-year-old Milly
OL,15,FDowler, Marsha McDonnell and Amelie
OL,16,FDelagrange, as well as the attempted
OL,17,Fmurder of Kate Sheedy.
