OL,3,CSerial killer Levi Bellfield blocked
OL,4,Cfrom having civil partnership amid new
OL,5,Claw
OL,7,FHe had recently submitted an
OL,8,Fapplication for a civil partnership,
OL,9,Fwhich is believed to have spurred the
OL,10,Fgovernment on to bring the restriction
OL,11,Fin from Friday.
OL,13,FLord Chancellor and Justice Secretary,
OL,14,FShabana Mahmood, said: "Victims should
OL,15,Fnot be tormented by seeing those who
OL,16,Fcommit the most depraved crimes enjoy
OL,17,Fthe moments in life that were stolen
OL,18,Ffrom their loved ones.
