OL,3,CSerial killer Levi Bellfield blocked
OL,4,Cfrom having civil partnership amid new
OL,5,Claw
OL,7,F"That is why I have acted as soon as
OL,8,Fpossible to stop these marriages and
OL,9,Fgive victims the support they deserve."
OL,11,FPreviously Bellfield had applied to
OL,12,Fmarry his girlfriend and made a bid
OL,13,Ffor legal aid to challenge a decision
OL,14,Fto block his marriage.
OL,16,FHe won a bid to be granted up to
OL,17,F#30,000 in legal aid after his lawyers
OL,18,Fcited the European Convention on Human
OL,19,FRights and the 1983 Marriage Act.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
