OL,3,CSerial killer Levi Bellfield blocked
OL,4,Cfrom having civil partnership amid new
OL,5,Claw
OL,7,FIt is understood he withdrew his
OL,8,Fapplication to get married but had
OL,9,Fsubmitted a new application for a
OL,10,Fcivil partnership in recent months.
OL,12,FThe new law, which is part of the
OL,13,FVictims and Prisoners Act, aims to
OL,14,F"deny the most heinous criminals from
OL,15,Fenjoying the important life events
OL,16,Fthey callously took from their
OL,17,Fvictims", the Ministry of Justice
OL,18,F(MoJ) said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
