OL,7,FThe Lord Chancellor will retain the
OL,8,Fright to allow ceremonies in the most
OL,9,Fexceptional circumstances, the MoJ
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FBellfield received a whole life
OL,13,Fsentence for the murder of Ms
OL,14,FMcDonnell, 19, in 2003, Ms Delagrange,
OL,15,F22, and the attempted murder of Ms
OL,16,FSheedy, 18, in 2004.
