OL,7,FHe was already serving his sentence
OL,8,Fwhen he went on trial for killing
OL,9,Fschoolgirl Milly, who was snatched
OL,10,Ffrom the street walking home from
OL,11,Fschool in Walton-on-Thames, Surrey, in
OL,12,FMarch 2002.
OL,14,FHe was found guilty of abducting and
OL,15,Fkilling the 13-year-old following a
OL,16,Ftrial at the Old Bailey in 2011.
